01:29:00,576 --> 01:29:14,922
I have a suggestion to remedy the language and that is to add the note of suggestion because I won't support this, Councilor, Mr. President, because on the grounds that that is a semi

1286
01:29:15,677 --> 01:29:16,517
judicial body.

1287
01:29:17,338 --> 01:29:23,220
It is to be independent from undue political influence, and I won't be a party to that.

1288
01:29:24,440 --> 01:29:25,541
Thank you, Councilor Del Rosso.

1289
01:29:25,901 --> 01:29:26,801
Vice President Marks.

1290
01:29:27,802 --> 01:29:32,443
Thank you, Mr. President, and I want to thank Councilor Felkel for offering this tonight.

