1295
01:29:45,190 --> 01:29:46,210
including this council.

1296
01:29:46,690 --> 01:29:51,792
There's been a number of meetings we've had in our council room in 207 where there was an overflow in the hall.

1297
01:29:52,572 --> 01:29:58,894
